The Pokémon Company iniciará en los próximos días un extenso stream de 24 horas para los juegos Pokémon Swords y Shield.

La compañía invitó a todos a participar del Stream. Sonia, la ayudante de la Profesora Magnolia, necesita ayuda para hacer una búsqueda en Glimwood Tangle, un bosque ubicado en una zona remota de Galar.

La transmisión iniciará el próximo viernes 4 de octubre podrán seguir el Stream por su canal de Twitch. https://swordshield.pokemon.com/en-us/pokemon-live-camera/?cid=&utm_source=tw&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=swordshield&utm_term=livestreamannounce

Cabe destacar que Pokémon Swords y Shield estará disponible a partir del 15 de noviembre por Nintendo Switch.

Super-late and Long Birthday post:

Other than me buying Switch as a gift to myself for my last year in my twenties (because I'm not a kid anymore so I buy my own gaming stuff now), I never really expected anything special. But if there's something I learned in the past ten years, it's that the best things in life are serendipitous.

I would like to thank my lady, my friends who greeted (and that one friend that conspired with my girl to surprise me), my family, and the Lord that brought all of these wonderful people into my life and gave me another year with them.  May You grant me more so I can spend more time with the ones I love, and may I witness the ways You'll bless them.

I completed Links’s Awakening last night!
✅1st Zelda I’ve ever beaten.
✅1st Switch game I’ve beaten.
I had tons of fun playing this!
Kinda sad that it’s over but I’ll still probably play and walk around the island to see what else I can find!
I’ve yet to try the dungeon builder so I’ll do that with my Link Amiibos!
In the past I’ve tried to limit the amount of time that I play on the Switch because I could sit there for hours and not mind one bit.
But I threw that idea out the window with this game!
I spent hours at night going around exploring and doing the story!
HIGHLY recommend you pick this game up for a fun chill gaming experience with wonderful moments!
